data.chText: 引入（新事物、思想或方法）；创新；改革
data.enText: to introduce new things, ideas, or ways of doing sth

data.chText: 我们必须不时地适应并创新，以确保在不断扩大的市场中取得成功。
data.enText: We must constantly adapt and innovate to ensure success in a growing market.

simple_means.memory_skill: in 使…；加以…；饰以… + nov 新 + ate 使… → 使焕然一新 → 革新，创新

means: 引入(新事物、思想或方法)

tr: bring something new to an environment
example: A new word processor was introduced

value.def: To innovate means to introduce changes and new ideas in the way something is done or made.

example.ex: ...his constant desire to innovate and experiment.
example.tran: 他不断进行创新和实验的渴望
